name: Hypolepis forzzae
remarks: doi:10.1640/0002-8444-108.4.151 The specific epithet honors Dr. Rafaela Campostrini Forzza (1972–), researcher and herbarium curator of Jardim Botânico do Rio de Janeiro (RB).

name: Hypolepis miodelii
distribution: Rio de Janeiro (Brazil Southeast, Brazil, Southern America)
remarks: doi:10.1640/0002-8444-108.4.151 The specific epithet honours Dr. Miodeli Nogueira Jr. (1981–), assistant professor and researcher at Universidade Federal da Paraíba.

name: Lindsaea pietrobomii
remarks: doi:10.1007/s12228-020-09606-z The specific epithet honours Dr. Marcio Roberto Pietrobom, eminent Brazilian pteridologist who has carried out several studies in the Brazilian Amazon.
